public abstract class AbstractUserData<DATA extends AbstractUserData<?>>
extends AbstractAdminData<DATA>

The class is used to define all user objects used to create / update and to export.

public void checkExport(ExportParser _exportParser)
                 throws matrix.util.MatrixException
